DataElement.preferredName: Bone Marrow Lymphoma Involvement Result Percentage Value
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A percentage value representing information related to the tissue occupying the spaces of bone and a personal medical history (an account of all medical events and problems a person has experienced) of the presence or involvement of neuroblastic cells.
